---
title: Chorizo Chili with Spiced Tortilla Chips
description: This quick chili packs a flavour punch given the short cook time! The oven-crisped tortilla chips will come in handy for dipping into that melty cheddar cheese topping!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chili-au-chorizo-9d25724f.jpg
